message.reasoning_content:
我们被要求根据给定的请求生成CopilotResponse。请求是中文的，任务是suggest_flowsheet_edits。我们需要输出一个JSON对象。

首先，分析请求：

- `project`: radishflow (必须写回)
- `task`: suggest_flowsheet_edits (必须写回)
- 上下文：有flowsheet_document，streams和units。诊断有三个错误，都针对compressor-3。
  1. COMPRESSOR_OUTLET_PRESSURE_TARGET_MISSING: "Review Compressor is configured for outlet pressure control but outlet pressure target is missing."
  2. COMPRESSOR_MINIMUM_FLOW_BYPASS_MISSING: anti-surge review requires minimum flow bypass percent missing.
  3. COMPRESSOR_EFFICIENCY_BASELINE_MISSING: efficiency percent input missing.

目标：生成proposed_actions，每个动作candidate_edit，提供补丁。补丁应该是最小的、可审查的、非执行的。只使用当前输入的信息。

必须输出JSON。结构：CopilotResponse。根据之前的描述，CopilotResponse应该包含：project, task, answers (至少1条), summary, issues, proposed_actions (至少1条), status, confidence, citations? 需要严格按照要求。

输出格式：
{
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "status": "partial", // 因为不能解决所有问题？但这里可以尝试解决所有问题，不过patch只是建议。
  "confidence": 0.9, // 等等
  "answers": [
    {
      "summary": "...",
      "issues": [...],
      "proposed_actions": [...]
    }
  ],
  "requires_confirmation": true
}

但是根据之前的示例，可能需要整体CopilotResponse有requires_confirmation: true。还要有citations。

检查要求：`citations` 应优先保持稳定顺序：直接诊断在前，目标对象artifact其次，supporting snapshot最后。所以每个问题可能需要citations。

可能回答结构：
{
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "answers": [
    {
      "id": "answer-1",
      "summary": "针对压缩机 compressor-3 的配置缺失问题，生成候选补丁。",
      "issues": [ ... ],
      "proposed_actions": [ ... ]
    }
  ],
  "status": "partial", // 可能因为只是建议，状态是partial，或者completed？但要求是证据不足时允许status=partial，这里证据足够，但patches是候选，不是解决问题，所以用partial表示未完全确认？但通常这些候选是给用户审查的，可以标记为partial，等待确认。也可能标记为completed。根据规则：证据不足时允许status=partial，但也应只把patch限制在当前被选中且有直接诊断支撑的局部对象上。我们有诊断，但图像只是建议，可以视为partial。不过更合理的是用"requires_confirmation": true来表明需要确认。status可以是"ok"如果已有提议？没有严格定义。我倾向于status: "partial"，表示建议并未应用，需要用户确认。并且在整体CopilotResponse中requires_confirmation: true。
  "requires_confirmation": true,
  "confidence": 0.9,
  "citations": [ ... ]
}

但是要求中说：“只输出一个 JSON 对象，结构必须满足 CopilotResponse”，但没有指定CopilotResponse的具体结构。从之前的例子中，我们能看到类似：
{
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "answers": [...],
  "requires_confirmation": true
}
等等。还有可能包含summary等。根据第2条，输出一个JSON对象，结构满足CopilotResponse。第10条："answers至少1条"，"summary必须先说明当前围绕哪个对象..", "issues只写真正触发patch的诊断..", "proposed_actions至少1条...". 所以顶层应该有answers数组。可能CopilotResponse就包含project, task, answers, status, confidence, requires_confirmation? 也可能还有citations。

结合第10条，citations应该放在哪里？可能是每个answer可选项，或者整体。根据第10条关于citations的描述，是在diagnostic -> artifact -> snapshot顺序，用于issues和candidate_edit的引用。例如在issue里可以有citations，candidate_edit里可以有citations。所以我们可以放在issue和proposed_action内部。

我们设计JSON如下：

{
  "project": "radishflow",
  "task": "suggest_flowsheet_edits",
  "status": "partial",
  "confidence": 0.9,
  "answers": [
    {
      "summary": "针对 Review Compressor (compressor-3) 在出口压力控制模式下缺少出口压力目标、缺少最小流量旁路百分比、以及缺少效率基线参数等问题，生成候选补丁。",
      "issues": [
        {
          "code": "COMPRESSOR_OUTLET_PRESSURE_TARGET_MISSING",
          "message": "Review Compressor is configured for outlet pressure control but outlet pressure target is missing.",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "citations": ["diag-1", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]
        },
        {
          "code": "COMPRESSOR_MINIMUM_FLOW_BYPASS_MISSING",
          "message": "Review Compressor anti-surge review requires minimum flow bypass percent, but the parameter is missing.",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "citations": ["diag-2", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]
        },
        {
          "code": "COMPRESSOR_EFFICIENCY_BASELINE_MISSING",
          "message": "Review Compressor is missing efficiency percent input required for current review baseline.",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "citations": ["diag-3", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]
        }
      ],
      "proposed_actions": [
        {
          "type": "candidate_edit",
          "title": "为出口压力控制模式补充目标压力占位符",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "rationale": "诊断 diag-1 指出压缩机配置为出口压力控制但缺少出口压力目标。需添加参数占位符以便用户设定目标。",
          "patch": {
            "parameter_placeholders": {
              "outlet_pressure_target_kpa": {
                "value": null,
                "description": "出口压力目标（kPa）",
                "required": true
              }
            }
          },
          "risk_level": "medium",
          "requires_confirmation": true,
          "citations": ["diag-1", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3", "snapshot-1"]
        },
        {
          "type": "candidate_edit",
          "title": "为抗喘振审查补充最小流量旁路百分比占位符",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "rationale": "诊断 diag-2 指出 anti-surge review 需要最小流量旁路百分比，但参数缺失。添加参数占位符。",
          "patch": {
            "parameter_placeholders": {
              "min_flow_bypass_percent": {
                "value": null,
                "description": "最小流量旁路百分比（%）",
                "required": true
              }
            }
          },
          "risk_level": "medium",
          "requires_confirmation": true,
          "citations": ["diag-2", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3", "snapshot-1"]
        },
        {
          "type": "candidate_edit",
          "title": "为审查基线补充效率百分比参数占位符",
          "target": "unit:compressor-3",
          "rationale": "诊断 diag-3 指出缺少效率百分比输入，为当前审查基线所需。添加参数占位符。",
          "patch": {
            "parameter_placeholders": {
              "efficiency_percent": {
                "value": null,
                "description": "压缩机效率百分比（%）",
                "required": true
              }
            }
          },
          "risk_level": "medium",
          "requires_confirmation": true,
          "citations": ["diag-3", "flowdoc-unit-compressor-3", "snapshot-1"]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "requires_confirmation": true
}

注意，第8条：只要存在candidate_edit，整体requires_confirmation必须为true，且每条candidate_edit.requires_confirmation也必须为true，我们满足了。

关于citations格式：诊断用"diag-1", "diag-2", "diag-3"；目标对象用"flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"（可能是"flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"）；snapshot用"snapshot-1"。需要定义citation ids。我们可以在回答中提供引用列表？但问题没有要求单独列出，可以在每个动作和问题的citations中直接使用这些值。不需要单独列出引用表。我们可以在answer级别加一个citations对象吗？但规范没有要求，重要的是在issue和action中有citations。另外需要确保引用顺序：先诊断，后artifact，最后snapshot。我们已经在citations数组中按顺序给出。还要保证支持清晰。没有问题。

目标target应为unit:compressor-3，在proposed_action中target字段可以直接写"compressor-3"。

还要注意patch的结构：使用parameter_placeholders是正确的，因为我们只是添加缺失的参数占位符，不需要具体值。对于出口压力控制模式，可能需要的是outlet_pressure_target，我们用一个合适的键。对于最小流量旁路，用min_flow_bypass_percent。效率参数用efficiency_percent。都是占位符。

"risk_level" 为medium，因为只是添加参数占位符，不会改变求解行为，直到用户填充值。所以中等风险。不是拓扑修改。

整体status: partial，因为建议还需要用户确认。

confidence: 0.9，因为诊断很明确。

最后，确保只输出JSON，没有markdown。所以直接给出JSON字符串。不使用代码块。

所以最终输出：
{"project":"radishflow","task":"suggest_flowsheet_edits","status":"partial","confidence":0.9,"answers":[{"summary":"针对 Review Compressor (compressor-3) 在出口压力控制模式下缺少出口压力目标、缺少最小流量旁路百分比、以及缺少效率基线参数等问题，生成候选补丁。","issues":[{"code":"COMPRESSOR_OUTLET_PRESSURE_TARGET_MISSING","message":"Review Compressor is configured for outlet pressure control but outlet pressure target is missing.","target":"unit:compressor-3","citations":["diag-1","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]},{"code":"COMPRESSOR_MINIMUM_FLOW_BYPASS_MISSING","message":"Review Compressor anti-surge review requires minimum flow bypass percent, but the parameter is missing.","target":"unit:compressor-3","citations":["diag-2","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]},{"code":"COMPRESSOR_EFFICIENCY_BASELINE_MISSING","message":"Review Compressor is missing efficiency percent input required for current review baseline.","target":"unit:compressor-3","citations":["diag-3","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3"]}],"proposed_actions":[{"type":"candidate_edit","title":"为出口压力控制模式补充目标压力占位符","target":"compressor-3","rationale":"诊断 diag-1 指出压缩机配置为出口压力控制但缺少出口压力目标。需添加参数占位符以便用户设定目标。","patch":{"parameter_placeholders":{"outlet_pressure_target_kpa":{"value":null,"description":"出口压力目标（kPa）","required":true}}},"risk_level":"medium","requires_confirmation":true,"citations":["diag-1","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3","snapshot-1"]},{"type":"candidate_edit","title":"为抗喘振审查补充最小流量旁路百分比占位符","target":"compressor-3","rationale":"诊断 diag-2 指出 anti-surge review 需要最小流量旁路百分比，但参数缺失。添加参数占位符。","patch":{"parameter_placeholders":{"min_flow_bypass_percent":{"value":null,"description":"最小流量旁路百分比（%）","required":true}}},"risk_level":"medium","requires_confirmation":true,"citations":["diag-2","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3","snapshot-1"]},{"type":"candidate_edit","title":"为审查基线补充效率百分比参数占位符","target":"compressor-3","rationale":"诊断 diag-3 指出缺少效率百分比输入，为当前审查基线所需。添加参数占位符。","patch":{"parameter_placeholders":{"efficiency_percent":{"value":null,"description":"压缩机效率百分比（%）","required":true}}},"risk_level":"medium","requires_confirmation":true,"citations":["diag-3","flowdoc-unit-compressor-3","snapshot-1"]}]}],"requires_confirmation":true}

检查要求：第一条：只输出一个JSON对象，结构满足CopilotResponse。我们有了。第二条：不要输出markdown代码块，不要输出JSON之外的解释。满足。第三条：project和task固定回写，已做。第四条：proposed_actions里的动作只能是candidate_edit，是的。第五条：只输出最小、可审查、非执行式的patch，只是占位符，符合。第六条：只使用当前输入里的诊断、FlowsheetDocument、选择集和快照，没有外部证据。第七条：candidate_edit存在，整体requires_confirmation和每个requires_confirmation均为true。第八条：如果有candidate_edit，整体true，每条true。第九条：证据充足，不用partial？我们用了partial，这也可以，因为提议没有应用。没问题。第十条：citations顺序：每个candidate_edit中先diag，然后flowdoc-unit，最后snapshot。OK。

target: 在proposed_actions中我们用了"compressor-3"，应该是unit id。符合。

patch结构：parameter_placeholders，合理。没有改变拓扑，risk_level=medium。

综上，输出JSON。没有多于内容。
